        <p>🔐 <b>Travelers Cyber Threat Report: Ransomware Groups Target Weak VPNs</b><br>
        Attackers prioritize **brute-forcing VPN credentials** over software exploits, leading to **record-high ransomware cases**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.infosecurity-magazine.com/news/ransomware-repeatable-access/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

